  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Clinical diagnosis of type 2 diabetes

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Impaired renal or liver function

          -  Cardiac disease

          -  Subjects with metal implants

          -  Hypertension

          -  Diabetes complications

          -  Exogenous insulin therapy
